        {
          "severity": "malignant obstruction",
          "criteria": "cancer confirmed, complete obstruction",
          "treatment": "Staging laparoscopy. Palliative gastrojejunostomy (laparoscopic). Endoscopic SEMS placement if poor surgical candidate. Chemotherapy."
